{
  "flow_name": "Nikigai Flow 1: Skills Discovery",
  "version": "1.0",
  "description": "Discover your natural skills through hobbies, proud moments, work experience, and learning.",
  "pillar": "skills",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "1.0",
      "step_order_index": 1,
      "assistant_prompt": "Let's discover your natural skills — the things you're naturally good at and love doing.\n\nWe'll explore your life through four lenses: hobbies, proud moments, work experience, and skills you've developed.\n\nFor each question, share 3-5 bullet points. The more detail, the richer the picture.\n\nReady to start?",
      "expected_inputs": [
        {
          "type": "single_select",
          "options": ["Yep!"]
        }
      ],
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_selection": "Yep!",
          "go_to": "2.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2.0",
      "step_order_index": 2,
      "assistant_prompt": "Let's start with **Childhood (Pre-school + Primary).**\n\nWhat did you *love doing most*? These can be games, hobbies, or activities that made you lose track of time.\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.hobbies.childhood",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "2.1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2.1",
      "step_order_index": 3,
      "assistant_prompt": "Now think of **High School.**\n\nWhat did you enjoy doing most for fun or self-expression?\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.hobbies.highschool",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "2.2"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2.2",
      "step_order_index": 4,
      "assistant_prompt": "Finally, from **18 to Now** — what activities, hobbies, or creative outlets light you up today?\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.hobbies.current",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "2.3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2.3",
      "step_order_index": 5,
      "assistant_postprocess": {
        "tag_from": [
          "life_map.hobbies.childhood",
          "life_map.hobbies.highschool",
          "life_map.hobbies.current"
        ],
        "cluster": {
          "target": "skills",
          "target_clusters_min": 2,
          "target_clusters_max": 5
        },
        "store_as": "skills.preview.from_hobbies"
      },
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "3.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3.0",
      "step_order_index": 6,
      "assistant_prompt": "Now let's recall moments that made you feel *alive* or *proud.*\n\nStarting with **Childhood**, what experiences or small wins made you feel happy, confident, or seen?\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.high_moments.childhood",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "3.1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3.1",
      "step_order_index": 7,
      "assistant_prompt": "During **High School**, what moments made you feel most alive or proud of yourself?\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.high_moments.highschool",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "3.2"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3.2",
      "step_order_index": 8,
      "assistant_prompt": "From **18 to Now**, what experiences gave you that same sense of pride, fulfillment, or aliveness?\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.high_moments.current",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "3.3"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "3.3",
      "step_order_index": 9,
      "assistant_postprocess": {
        "tag_from": [
          "life_map.hobbies.childhood",
          "life_map.hobbies.highschool",
          "life_map.hobbies.current",
          "life_map.high_moments.childhood",
          "life_map.high_moments.highschool",
          "life_map.high_moments.current"
        ],
        "cluster": {
          "target": "skills",
          "target_clusters_min": 2,
          "target_clusters_max": 5
        },
        "store_as": "skills.preview.from_hobbies_and_moments"
      },
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "4.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4.0",
      "step_order_index": 10,
      "assistant_prompt": "Let's explore your work and projects.\n\nAcross your jobs, projects, or creative pursuits, what have you **enjoyed doing most**?\n\nThink of times you felt in flow or energized by what you were doing.\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.experience.enjoyed_most",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "4.1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4.1",
      "step_order_index": 11,
      "assistant_prompt": "When you look at those experiences, what *skills or patterns* do you notice repeating?\n\nExample: leadership, communication, creativity, empathy.\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.experience.repeating_skills",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "5.0"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5.0",
      "step_order_index": 12,
      "assistant_prompt": "What **skills have you loved to develop**?\n\nThink about skills you've intentionally worked on — through courses, practice, or personal curiosity.\n\nShare 3-5 bullets.",
      "expected_inputs": ["text_list"],
      "store_as": "life_map.learning.skills_developed",
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "5.1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "5.1",
      "step_order_index": 13,
      "assistant_postprocess": {
        "tag_from": [
          "life_map.hobbies.childhood",
          "life_map.hobbies.highschool",
          "life_map.hobbies.current",
          "life_map.high_moments.childhood",
          "life_map.high_moments.highschool",
          "life_map.high_moments.current",
          "life_map.experience.enjoyed_most",
          "life_map.experience.repeating_skills",
          "life_map.learning.skills_developed"
        ],
        "cluster": {
          "target": "skills",
          "target_clusters_min": 3,
          "target_clusters_max": 6
        },
        "store_as": "skills.final"
      },
      "next_step_rules": [
        {
          "on_success": "complete"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
